  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Multimodal analgesia is a rational approach to treat various components of postoperative
      pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Local anesthetic wound infiltration is widely recognized as a useful adjunct during
      multimodal postoperative pain management whether given before operation or perioperatively.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
